&lt;p data-start=&quot;358&quot; data-end=&quot;676&quot;&gt;The Parts Runner is responsible for the timely and accurate delivery of parts, tools, and materials between the warehouse, job sites, and vendor locations. This role is critical to maintaining efficient daily operations by ensuring technicians and installers have the materials they need when and where they need them.&lt;/p&gt;
