&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;6nq8o9&quot; data-start=&quot;814&quot; data-end=&quot;943&quot;&gt;Ensure accuracy of all deliveries and pickups, including verifying quantities and signing invoices or delivery documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;19atri9&quot; data-start=&quot;944&quot; data-end=&quot;1042&quot;&gt;Perform quality checks to confirm parts and materials are in good condition prior to delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1m2j0sw&quot; data-start=&quot;1043&quot; data-end=&quot;1130&quot;&gt;Safely load and unload materials, following proper lifting and handling procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ng7tna&quot; data-start=&quot;1131&quot; data-end=&quot;1231&quot;&gt;Assist with organizing, stocking, and maintaining warehouse inventory when not on delivery runs.&lt;/li&gt;
